                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18441125-157-offence-1 t18441125-cd-51"></join>21st of Nov</rs>., 4 handkerchiefs, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1 pair of shoes, 85.; the goods of <persName id="t18441125-name-921" type="victimName">
